WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
<i>[office noise]</i>

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
Michael: Uh-oh, okay, okay, nobody panic.

00:06.000 --> 00:08.000
Michael: Listen up, listen up.

00:06.000 --> 00:08.000
<i>[people running and shouting]</i>

00:08.000 --> 00:10.000
Michael: Everyone, follow me to the shelter.

00:10.000 --> 00:12.000
Michael: We've got enough food for 14 days.

00:12.000 --> 00:15.000
Michael: After that, we have a difficult conversation.

00:15.000 --> 00:17.000
<i>[fan humming]</i>

00:15.000 --> 00:18.000
Dwight: My bad. Space heater and fan were both on high,

00:18.000 --> 00:20.000
Dwight: plugged into the same outlet, so...

00:20.000 --> 00:21.500
<i>[server beeping]</i>

00:20.000 --> 00:23.000
Ryan: Uh, it's saying the server went down.

00:23.000 --> 00:25.000
Ryan: Does anybody know that password?

00:25.000 --> 00:27.000
Ryan: Because otherwise we can't do any work.

00:27.000 --> 00:29.000
Michael: Uh-oh, try password.

00:29.000 --> 00:31.000
Ryan: Nope.

00:31.000 --> 00:35.000
Michael: Try zero, zero, zero. Zero, zero, zero.

00:35.000 --> 00:36.000
Ryan: No.

00:36.000 --> 00:40.000
Michael: Okay, now try zero, zero, zero. Zero, zero, one.

00:40.000 --> 00:42.000
Ryan: Okay, I'm not doing every number.

00:42.000 --> 00:45.000
Jim: Wait, um, does anyone remember when it was set up?

00:45.000 --> 00:47.000
Dwight: Uh, it was like eight years ago.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.000
Kevin: Lord of the Rings stuff?

00:49.000 --> 00:50.000
Michael: I don't know.

00:50.000 --> 00:52.000
Michael: I'm just trying to think of things that were happening at the time.

00:52.000 --> 00:54.000
Michael: Um, everyone was getting their driver's license.

00:54.000 --> 00:57.000
Jim: Why don't we just call the IT guy who set it up?

00:57.000 --> 00:59.000
Jim: What's the name of the guy in the glasses again?

00:59.000 --> 01:02.000
Michael: Okay, moving backwards, our IT guys have been.

01:02.000 --> 01:06.000
Michael: Glasses, turban, ear hair, fatty three, shorts, fatty two,

01:06.000 --> 01:08.000
Michael: lozenge, and fatso.

01:08.000 --> 01:11.000
Dwight: I think lozenge is the one who installed it.

01:11.000 --> 01:13.000
Michael: I got it. Try, um...

01:13.000 --> 01:15.000
Dwight: Cough, cough, cough, cough.

01:15.000 --> 01:18.000
Michael: You know what? It made me laugh when I heard it,

01:18.000 --> 01:20.000
Michael: but Pam got really offended.

01:20.000 --> 01:22.000
Michael: Big boobs.

01:22.000 --> 01:25.000
Oscar: Trauma coin? Nosey?

01:26.000 --> 01:28.000
Pam: You're typing big boobs?

01:28.000 --> 01:30.000
Michael: I'm trying everything.

01:30.000 --> 01:32.000
Dwight: Try big boobs with a Z.

01:32.000 --> 01:34.000
Ryan: That's the password. We're in.

01:34.000 --> 01:35.000
Jim: All right.

01:35.000 --> 01:36.000
Oscar: Wow. Yes.

01:36.000 --> 01:39.000
Michael: The important thing is, this kept us secure, people.
